    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527803",
        "quote": "For millions of years, this world has been a great gift to nearly everything living on it, a planet whose atmosphere, temperature, air, water, seasons, and weather were precisely calibrated to allow us - the big us, including forests and oceans, species large and small - to flourish.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527803"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Gift",
                "url": "/topics/gift"
            },
            {
                "name": "Atmosphere",
                "url": "/topics/atmosphere"
            },
            {
                "name": "Allow",
                "url": "/topics/allow"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527804",
        "quote": "The Earth we evolved to inhabit is turning into something more turbulent and unreliable at a pace too fast for most living things to adapt to.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527804"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Living",
                "url": "/topics/living"
            },
            {
                "name": "More",
                "url": "/topics/more"
            },
            {
                "name": "Inhabit",
                "url": "/topics/inhabit"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527805",
        "quote": "Everywhere people are at work to build a better world in which we - and some of the beauty of this world - will be guaranteed to survive. Everywhere they are at war with the forces threatening us and the planet.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527805"
        },
        "topics": [
