    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527806",
        "quote": "The world you live in is not a given; much of what is best in it has been built through the struggles of passionate activists over the last centuries. They won us many freedoms and protected many beauties. Count those gifts among your growing heap.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527806"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
