                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527809",
        "quote": "The oil dinosaurs want to win so badly in my home state because what happens here matters everywhere. The nation often follows where California goes.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527809"
