    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527800",
        "quote": "Revolution is a phase, a mood, like spring, and just as spring has its buds and showers, so revolution has its ebullience, its bravery, its hope, and its solidarity. Some of these things pass.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527800"
