                "url": "/topics/rebuild"
            },
            {
                "name": "Other",
                "url": "/topics/other"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527808",
        "quote": "It's hardly surprising that the corporate aliens lie when it comes to the relationship between doing something about climate change and the economy.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527808"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Change",
                "url": "/topics/change"
            },
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527785",
        "quote": "We have a real role in how our own collective lives, our nation, and our world and society turn out. Seizing those opportunities is important, and disasters are sometimes one of those opportunities.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527785"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Role",
                "url": "/topics/role"
            },
            {
                "name": "Nation",
                "url": "/topics/nation"
            },
            {
                "name": "Lives",
                "url": "/topics/lives"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527780",
        "quote": "Having the right to show up and speak are basic to survival, to dignity, and to liberty.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527780"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Survival",
                "url": "/topics/survival"
            },
            {
                "name": "Liberty",
                "url": "/topics/liberty"
            },
            {
                "name": "Having",
                "url": "/topics/having"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527786",
        "quote": "It's not that bad things never happen. But there's a pattern in which most people are calm, resourceful, altruistic, and they improvise emergency systems that work really well - whether it's getting the babies out of a collapsed hospital or putting together a community kitchen to feed everybody for the next few months.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527786"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Bad",
                "url": "/topics/bad"
