                "url": "/topics/communications"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527796",
        "quote": "The exercise of democracy begins as exercise, as walking around, becoming familiar with the streets, comfortable with strangers, able to imagine your own body as powerful and expressive rather than a pawn.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Rebecca Solnit",
            "url": "/quotes/rebecca_solnit_527796"
        },
